meaning: Good tried to delete/free a navigation mesh parser object, but it does not exist or has already been freed.
causes: The passed RID (Resource ID) was never created or was already freed.
The parser object was already deleted elsewhere before free_rid was called.
Incorrect usage of the API by freeing an invalid RID.
fixes: Make sure that the RID you are using is valid by doing error checks.
Check if the parser object exists.
notes: This error normally does not appear in standard GDScript/C# usage.
NavigationServer is managed by Godot, user code should not cause this error to happen.
